    subgraph "会话 A"
        A1[AI 发现调试技巧] --> A2[MemoryWrite]
    end
    
    subgraph "持久化存储"
        A2 --> M[(MEMORY.md / topics.md)]
    end
    
    subgraph "会话 B (新启动)"
        M --> B1[AutoMemoryManager 加载索引]
        B1 --> B2[System Prompt 注入]
        B2 --> B3[AI 获得历史经验]
    end
```

